{"tid":972185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：我不是親中，我是中　指「歷史會證明我是對」","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T10:05:39.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7013a2255afb4558743d3a26487642b30398a340","tid":972185,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190107/s00001/822da0fff0ea58bd95bbf76e424539d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190107%2Fs00001%2F822da0fff0ea58bd95bbf76e424539d4.jpg&h=539fe5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任建制派立法會議員多年的梁美芬，去年更成為了基本法委員會委員。不過她強調自己「不是親中」，「我是中，我的心真真正正為中國做事」，又說「相信歷史會證明我是對的」。<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：梁振英：一國兩制實踐成功國際公認　籲台灣人多來港直接了解<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬近日接受網媒「堅料網」訪問，提到2008年當選立法會議員時，有朋友問她為何「親中」，但她認為對方「用錯字」，稱「我不是親中，我是中，我的心真真正正為中國做事，我不是為了親她&hellip;&hellip;即使在香港大家不理解，因為某些issue（議題）我變成unpopular（不受歡迎），但我相信歷史會證明我是對的」。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬強調，她也曾批評國家，如1993年深圳致麗玩具廠大火時，她大罵深圳當局，認為「貢獻不代表沒有批評」。<br />\n<br />\n問到為何市民要認識《基本法》，梁美芬以特區護照作例，「這本護照現在我們香港人好喜歡，很多地方不需要簽證，是中國給我們，我認為是一份特別的禮物」。她又反問：「沒有《基本法》，究竟我們的身分是什麼？沒有《基本法》，可能我們要的是中華人民共和國的護照，下面沒有香港特別行政區。」<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬在facebook分享該訪問，留言：「從頭認識梁美芬。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190107/s00001/1546833641066/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190107%2Fs00001%2F1546833641066%2F&d=eJNfJf4F4gWZ4jv3F0VDuQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=9fea635c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190107%2Fs00001%2F1546833641066%2F&h=a8e0341a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190107/s00001/1546833641066/</a>"},{"pid":"b8cc18766a71cac4258ff1fb12369363b3d62ff6","tid":972185,"uid":50041,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"搞撚笑,你只係一隻老鼠,歷史上邊有你既位置,睇到自己咁高"},{"pid":"b8f1c33b79e9934ff59d681a5769cf474f51d4f8","tid":972185,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"梁美芬：中國人民大學法律碩士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071213ab25c79a0e503cd2ee5040ca12b516661f","tid":972185,"uid":163801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"到歷史證明佢錯又點?? 咪又係一早去咗外國嘆世界. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacac802c7e33f56fa895bd6045de486837d951c","tid":972185,"uid":44358,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"親中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊有資格，最多奶共啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbe267c4a2fe9ebfdd7472e406416e5a3a16b38","tid":972185,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"唔舐邊有今日"},{"pid":"e36d569775fa57d9e955e48c1d70ee6093e5659c","tid":972185,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"支那都冇能力拎免簽<br />\n佢點樣送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBNO就真係英國送嘅禮物啦"},{"pid":"1c48995cf8144089f4e242145da0a14ff87b8c0b","tid":972185,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cacac802c7e33f56fa895bd6045de486837d951c","tid":972185,"uid":44358,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"親中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊有資格，最多奶共啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"中point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2093a7dd20bc3f603fa916cfd399caeee2e72ed","tid":972185,"uid":50310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:29:17.0